Protocol sterilization seeds


Sterilization of seeds:

-	Add 1 drop of 70%EtOH
-	Immediately add 1ml 1/10 bleach
o	Soak 10min
-	Wash three times with sterile water

Too make the plant TMV free do this before the sterilization of the seeds:
-	Soak the seeds in 18% HCL for 10 min
-	Rinse with sterile water
-	Soak the seeds in 10% TSP for 15 min
-	Rinse with sterile water
